org.dotplot.image
Interface IROIResult

All Known Implementing Classes:
ROIResult
public interface IROIResult

Implementing objects are created when the user has selected a region of interest. Given this roi, the corresponding files and lines are returned by the DotPlot.

Author:
Tobias Gesellchen
